  "3146120": {
    "name": "寂静之国的波斯菊",
    "steam_appid": 3146120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/3b4c26925121cd24327448ef16e095e0.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=800 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/3b4c26925121cd24327448ef16e095e0.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/3b4c26925121cd24327448ef16e095e0.mp4?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/8b1139bd4e33de03f980f67816b62eab.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/8b1139bd4e33de03f980f67816b62eab.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进阿雅萨的怪异世界,这是一个将任务、恐怖和谜题融合成一段令人难以忘怀的旅程的黑暗故事。故事没有一句台词,而是通过哑剧、超现实意象和科米塔斯创作的配乐来讲述。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将穿越六个象征性的土地:信仰、希望、爱、贪婪、冷漠和背叛—每个土地都被黑暗所腐蚀。你所做的每一个选择,每一个同情或冷漠的行为,都可能导致意想不到的结局。你会恢复平衡还是成为你想要击败的力量？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/56bac0945a728402972fa0600a2d0ac0.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/56bac0945a728402972fa0600a2d0ac0.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倒置世界曾经处于平衡状态,在绝对者塔斯的注视下,光与影共存。但现在,战争打破了这种和谐。随着黑暗的蔓延,阿亚萨必须穿越被贪婪、背叛和冷漠蹂躏的土地,寻找隐藏在爱、信仰和希望领域的塔斯之光的残余。这不仅仅是一场生存的追求,而是一场灵魂之战,战场就在其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/3dc7215654bacb2d0d0891e9a41d78f0.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/3dc7215654bacb2d0d0891e9a41d78f0.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗而超现实的世界 – 探索令人难忘的美丽土地,灵感来自蒂姆·伯顿、勒内·拉卢、罗伯特·萨哈基恩茨和宫崎骏。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光影机制 – 使用光来揭示路径、激活古代机器并驱散黑暗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战谜题 – 解决考验逻辑、时机和创造力的复杂环境谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特能力 – 在解决谜题时,在游戏过程中解锁来自好土地的力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式氛围 – 通过哑剧、视觉象征和深刻的情感配乐讲述的无对话叙事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/eedfcf33355248b909a45196ce28736d.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/eedfcf33355248b909a45196ce28736d.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Ayasa》中，你将穿越危险的国度，运用光与影解开谜题、躲避敌人并发现隐藏的秘密。每个区域都有独特的挑战，结合平台跳跃与探索，让你在冒险中时刻保持警觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上这段难忘的冒险旅程，揭开颠倒世界的秘密。你能恢复平衡，还是会被黑暗吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/e106bcf66165f7b5b4c106d1503569d4.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/e106bcf66165f7b5b4c106d1503569d4.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 Ayasa 的能力穿越危险的地形、避开危险并解决谜题。每片土地都带来独特的机制和道德选择,你的良心决定了世界的命运。该游戏将平台、探索和环境故事融为一体,带来难忘的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艺术指导 每一帧都是一幅充满象征意义、超现实主义和黑色情感的画作。世界的美丽充满了忧郁,使用简约而有力的调色板来唤起惊奇和恐惧。关卡感觉充满活力,每个地点都讲述着自己的无声故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/db39ccec52bdd06d7fd297936d913e56.poster.avif?t=1770068315\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146120/extras/db39ccec52bdd06d7fd297936d913e56.webm?t=1770068315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ayasa:沉默的阴影邀请玩家进入一个世界,在这个世界里,最小的行为可以改变一切,而结局取决于指导你选择的心。</p>",
